CommentText: I purchased this item & was disappointed upon receiving it. First, the item did not arrive in a proper, sealed box, which made it feel like a used or returned product rather than a new one. After spending over $200, I expected the item to be in new condition, but it came in an open box with no instructions or SKU numbers for registration. This was quite frustrating and not what i had anticipated feom a new purchase.

Item arrived damaged though seemed properly packaged. Seller accepted the return, but then did not send a return shipping label for almost 10 days (and only then after escalating to an eBay account manager for Dyson). This will impact my decision to purchase a replacement item.
